    	<li>The next step is to add your artist profile. This includes your legal name and contact information.</li>
    	<li>You will then select what type of art you would like to submit. If a submission fee is required, you will be prompted to pay the submission fee before you can apply.</li>
		<li>Invited artists will enter a discount code to waive the submission fee.</li>
